{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781367642420,"sessionID":"ses_13e377e8fffeBUJXd02f1iJrmW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_2yLIXV77FpXLuTiP97IOjevg","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-research agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-research/SKILL.md and execute the research loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55fast-1781367602693-9nehlm\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: research\n  config.maxIterations: 5\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast. Do not touch any path outside /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast","specFolder":".opencode/specs/ski