{"type":"text","timestamp":1781368059541,"sessionID":"ses_13e377e8fffeBUJXd02f1iJrmW","part":{"id":"prt_ec1cf1dd8001cpP10uyevS6jOZ","messageID":"msg_ec1ceef1d001FmNgv5xGzkoDpZ","sessionID":"ses_13e377e8fffeBUJXd02f1iJrmW","type":"text","text":"## Goal\n- Execute `deep-research` fan-out lineage `gpt55fast` for `ui-ux-pro-max` merge recommendations into `sk-interface-design`.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- Write outputs only under `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast`.\n- Do not run `resolveArtifactRoot`; bind `artifact_dir` directly to the fanout override path.\n- Run `phase_init`, `phase_main_loop` to convergence or `config.maxIterations: 5`, then `phase_synthesis`.\n- Final output when complete must be exactly: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast`.\n- Research-only: do not modify `.opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/`.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Read `.opencode/skills/deep-research/SKILL.md`, command contract, auto YAML, state/convergence references.\n- Bound `artifact_dir` to `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast`.\n- Created lineage dirs: `prompts/`, `iterations/`, `deltas/`.\n- Completed `phase_init`:\n  - `deep-research-config.json`\n  - `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - `deep-research-strategy.md`\n  - `deep-research-findings-registry.json`\n  - `deep-research-dashboard.md`\n- Completed iteration 1 and wrote:\n  - `prompts/iteration-001.md`\n  - `iterations/iteration-001.md`\n  - `deltas/iter-001.jsonl`\n  - appended iteration record to `deep-research-state.jsonl`\n  - updated `deep-research-strategy.md`\n- Iteration 1 findings:\n  - External repo is data-driven design intelligence: styles, colors, typography, UX, charts, stacks, reasoning datasets.\n  - Reusable source of truth is `src/ui-ux-pro-max/data`, `scripts`, `templates`.\n  - External installer/platform plumbing should be skipped for direct merge.\n  - MIT license permits merge/adaptation with copyright + permission notice preservation.\n  - `sk-interface-design` is intentionally lean and should not receive a direct data dump into `SKILL.md`.\n\n### In Progress\n- Iteration 2 source inspection of external CSV/data classes.\n- Already read representative files:\n  - `products.csv`, `styles.csv`, `colors.csv`, `typography.csv`, `ux-guidelines.csv`, `ui-reasoning.csv`, `charts.csv`, `landing.csv`, `app-interface.csv`, `icons.csv`, `react-performance.csv`, `design.csv`.\n- Need externalize iteration 2 artifacts and state.\n\n### Blocked\n- `(none)`\n\n## Key Decisions\n- Do not spawn `opencode run` from inside OpenCode; auto YAML notes a `cli-opencode` self-invocation guard.\n- Skip workflow save/git/spec-writeback steps because user allowed writes only inside lineage directory.\n- Treat external CLI/marketplace/platform installer plumbing as `SKIP` for direct merge.\n\n## Next Steps\n- 1. Finish iteration 2: classify CSV/data asset classes as ADOPT/ADAPT/SKIP and write `iteration-002.md`, `iter-002.jsonl`, append state.\n- 2. Continue iterations 3-5 or stop earlier if convergence gates pass.\n- 3. Write `research.md` / synthesis under lineage dir only.\n- 4. Verify all required lineage artifacts exist and final line: `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast`.\n\n## Critical Context\n- Memory trigger with provided session failed: `sessionId \"fanout-gpt55fast-1781367602693-9nehlm\" does not match a server-managed session`; retried memory without MCP session binding.\n- Memory context returned no prior packet-specific research results.\n- `resource-map.md` not present; coverage gate skipped.\n- `plan.md` not found in packet.\n- External repo actual path is `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main`; initial literal path under `002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/external` found no files.\n- Config/session identifiers:\n  - `session_id`: `fanout-gpt55fast-1781367602693-9nehlm`\n  - executor: `cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast`\n  - max iterations: `5`\n  - convergence threshold: `0.05`\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast`: lineage artifact root.\n- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/spec.md`: research scope and success criteria.\n- `.opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/SKILL.md`: target skill shape and constraints.\n- `.opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/references/design_principles.md`: existing design guidance to compare against.\n- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main`: external repo source.\n- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/LICENSE`: MIT attribution requirements.\n- `.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/src/ui-ux-pro-max/data`: external data assets under iteration 2 review.","time":{"start":1781368036824,"end":1781368059537},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_062f358114e150ae016a2d84e4ce308191b2ee099ef93a8454","phase":"final_answer"}}}}
