s native .opencode packaging; external installer plumbing targets many assistants and adds maintenance burden.\",\"evidence\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/skill.json:20-40\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-13T16:24:10Z\",\"durationMs\":30000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781367602693-9nehlm\",\"generation\":1}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter001-asset-taxonomy\",\"label\":\"External repo is data-driven design intelligence with styles, colors, typography, UX, chart, stack, and reasoning datasets.\",\"iteration\":1,\"source\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/README.md:151-159\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter001-source-layout\",\"label\":\"Reusable source of truth is src/ui-ux-pro-max/data, scripts, and templates; installer/platform folders are downstream packaging surfaces.\",\"iteration\":1,\"source\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/CLAUDE.md:30-60\"}\n{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-iter001-mit-license\",\"label\":\"MIT permits merge/adaptation with copyright and permission notice preservation.\",\"iteration\":1,\"source\":\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/LICENSE:1-13\"}\n{\"type\":\"ruled_out\",\"direction\":\"Installer/platform-template direct merge\",\"reason\":\"Packaging plumbing does not improve sk-interface-design guidance and conflicts with lean house packaging.\",\"iteration\":1}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":5,"totalLines":5,"truncated":false}},"title":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/002-ui-ux-pro-max-merge-research/research/lineages/gpt55fast/deltas/iter-001.jsonl","time":{"start":1781368192053,"end":1781368192057}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0e9355728a50daab016a2d857ff0188191a2f8ec7262e92286"}},"id":"prt_ec1d17c33001I