rc/ui-ux-pro-max/templates/base/skill-content.md:77-109\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-13T16:32:00Z\",\"durationMs\":120000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-gpt55fast-1781367602693-9nehlm\",\"generation\":1}\n {\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":1,\"iteration\":3,\"mode\":\"research\",\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"House layout, stack ownership, and attribution\",\"findingsCount\":10,\"newInfoRatio\":0.46,\"noveltyJustification\":\"This iteration resolved the target layout, stack ownership boundary, and mixed-license attribution path using current target metadata plus representative stack CSV evidence.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"How should reusable external assets fit the house skill structure without making SKILL.md too large?\",\"Should stack-specific CSVs be adopted, adapted, or left to sk-code ownership?\",\"What license and attribution path is required for mixing MIT external content with the existing Apache-2.0 vendored Anthropic skill?\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"Add optional references/design_intelligence subtree and keep SKILL.md lean.\",\"Skip direct stack CSV merge; adapt only cross-cutting design quality fragments; leave implementation stack expansion to future sk-code work.\",\"Keep Apache-2.0 notice and add separate MIT notice/file for ui-ux-pro-max-derived content.\"],\"sourcesQueried\":[\".opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/README.md\",\".opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/LICENSE.txt\",\".opencode/skills/sk-interface-design/graph-metadata.json\",\".opencode/skills/sk-code/SKILL.md\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/LICENSE\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/src/ui-ux-pro-max/data/stacks/react.csv\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/148-sk-interface-design/external/ui-ux-pro-max-skill-main/src/ui-ux-pro-max/data/stacks/nextjs.csv\",\".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-o